This directory contains scripts to manipulate genealogical data 
available in the wiki site Rodovid (en.rodovid.org)

extract_numbers.pl is a Perl script to extract a complete set of files. 
The command line should contain the Rodovid Person number as the only argument.
The complete set of files, one per person that link to the input person will be written in the current directory. In addition, a file UniquePersons will contain all the numbers of the Person given as input. 
